  "instructions": [
    "Combine fish with apple cider vinegar and marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Heat a wok or large skillet over high heat. Add coconut cream and chicken bouillon cubes to the pan.",
    "Once the mixture is hot, add minced garlic and ginger; cook until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
